1938    Born in Lima.
1956-61 Studied agricultural engineering at National Agrarian
        University of La Molina, Lima.
1984-89 Rector of National Agrarian University, La Molina, and
        president of National Assembly of University Rectors.
1989    Formed Cambio (Change) 90 party.
1990    Elected president.
