<DATELINE>
   MONTREAL
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
CANADIAN Pacific Forest Products suffered a loss of CDollars 571.5m
(USDollars 492.6m), or 13 cents a share, in 1991, after special pre-tax
charges of CDollars 528m to cover mill shutdowns and a write-down of its
