over Pounds 660m, writes Simon London.
Announcing an interim loss of Pounds 56.1m for the six months to the end of
September, against Pounds 58.3m last time, Mr Louis Sherwood, chairman, said
that senior lenders have agreed to continue rolling up interest and
repayments of principle. The position will be reviewed again in December.
While interest costs of Pounds 47.3m (Pounds 43.3m) were charged, no cash
