excellent long term returns in a very competitive market place, with
millions of satisfied policyholders.
Policyholders enjoy the protection of a regulatory framework that has never
been stronger. Selling practices, which Mr Rigg attacks, are in particular
closely controlled and monitored. Great emphasis is placed on suitability
and the long-term nature of the contracts.
