certain to be added to poll tax bills for the additional costs incurred by
non-payment or delayed payments. He said figures released recently by the
Chartered Institute for Public Finance and Accountancy confirmed Labour's
claims that final poll tax bills for 1992-93 would near Pounds 300 and not
